:"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757296194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757296194","tinyui":"/x/QgBZp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757296194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757296194/Archived+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757296194"}},{"id":"3771367425","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3771367425","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzc3MTM2NzQyNQ==","status":"current","title":"CMB","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":172688587},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3771367425/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3771367425/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3771367425/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3771367425/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3771367425","tinyui":"/x/AYDK4","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3771367425","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3771367425/CMB","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3771367425"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"1932161e-5345-41d4-8f44-88a62c0e7003\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para CMB, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"62e92cf23cc20c06c8ae81e4\" ri:local-id=\"608eced8-b90a-4f39-a3ff-0c97b974ec32\" /></ac:link> .</p><p>Las horas estimadas son: </p><p>Fecha de Inicio: <strong>Martes</strong> <time datetime=\"2025-03-04\" /></p><p>Fecha estimada de entrega: <strong>Lunes </strong><time datetime=\"2025-04-21\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 152.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 485.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 121.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p><strong>billing-service</strong></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar columna en la tabla Productos para diferenciar si la extracci&oacute;n es por QR</p><p><em>La columna deber&iacute;a ser Is_QR_Cashout</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Revisar el endpoint de creaci&oacute;n de productos para que se creen con esta flag nueva</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>commerce-suite</strong></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar la l&oacute;gica en el portal de Boca-Web para generar el QR en el caso de que el producto tenga la flag Is_QR_Cashout </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar l&oacute;gica de websockets para renderizar voucher cuando llegue la notificaci&oacute;n exitosa</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Llamar al endpoint de generar el QR para cada entidad</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>epos-service</strong></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar un nuevo modelo de cashout qr</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar endpoint para generar QR</p><p><em>Esto va a tomar todos los datos de desembolso para generar el QR de cada entidad</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Crear endpoint para confirmar QR de desembolso</p><p><em>Vamos a precisar un endpoint nuevo para notificar al facturador que se hizo el desembolso</em></p><p><em>Hay que rechazar todo lo que no sea d&eacute;bito en cuenta</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">32</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Modificar endpoint de transfer para diferenciar que es un desembolso por QR</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar comunicaci&oacute;n con endpoint del facturador para comunicar el desembolso</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar comunicaci&oacute;n de Websocket con commerce-suite para notificar el estado del desembolso</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>billing-service-public-proxy</strong></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar l&oacute;gica del decode para llamar al endpoint de confirmaci&oacute;n del QR de desembolso</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>General</strong></p></td><td><p>Creaci&oacute;n y revisi&oacute;n de PRs, soluci&oacute;n de comments, armado de ramas, deploy a stagin</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">230</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">34</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">264</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3771432961"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":15},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3771432961/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3771432961/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3771432961/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3771432961/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3771432961","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3771432961/Backend+CMB+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3771432961","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3771432961","tinyui":"/x/AYDL4","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}